# SophiaAgent Environment Variables
# Run `sophia init` to configure interactively, or set these manually.

# LLM Provider — pick ONE of the blocks below:

# --- OpenAI ---
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# SOPHIA_MODEL=gpt-4o

# --- Anthropic Claude ---
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# SOPHIA_MODEL=claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022

# --- OpenAI-compatible (vLLM / Ollama / DeepSeek / Qwen) ---
# SOPHIA_BASE_URL=https://YOUR_HOST/v1
# SOPHIA_API_KEY=your-key-here
# SOPHIA_MODEL=your-model-name

# Optional: Academic literature search
# SEMANTIC_SCHOLAR_API_KEY=

# Optional: workspace override
# SOPHIA_WORKSPACE=~/SophiaWorkspace
